<h1>Support Page</h1>
<p>
    Mindfulnest strives to provide support to all our employees through an excellent team of IT support staff. They have been extremely grateful and have collaborated the below support forum if there are any issues faced by the on-site staff whist managing books and members.
</p>
<div>
    <strong>Issues with creating a book</strong>
    <p>Most common issue with book creation that admin faces are:</p>
