</div>
<div>
    <strong>Common Issues with creation of book copy</strong>
    <p>Most common issues with creation of book copy  that admin faces are:</p>
    <img src="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1Lfqnp_okH0_GwcBZbGhxS07DR-6x_PmE" align="middle" width="500px"
         title="Book Copy">
    <p>
        <ol>
            <li>
                Name for a book copy is a mandatory field, so you must always provide a valid value for it.
            </li>
            <li>
                Date of arrival is a mandatory field, so you must always provide a valid value for it. It is also worth noting that date of arrival cannot be a future date.
            </li>
            <li>
                Aisle location specifies the location of the book and it only accepts numeric values.
            </li>
        </ol>
    </p>
</div>
